sub_title: Founder & CEO @ Saaslaunch.io | Early Stage Tech Startups | Keynote Speaker
summary:
Denise, the visionary force behind Saaslaunch.io, stands at the helm as the founder and CEO of the prestigious boutique management consulting firm. 

Boasting an extraordinary career spanning over a decade, Denise has triumphed in (Tech) sales leaving her mark in diverse corners of the world, from the captivating landscapes of Equatorial Guinea in Africa to the enchanting shores of Ireland, Spain, Curacao & the Netherlands. 

Along her journey, she has worked for industry titans like Linkedin and Oracle, driving growth and elevating revenue quarter after quarter.

Today, Denise stands as a guiding light for ambitious startups, empowering them to soar to new heights. 
As a beacon of knowledge and expertise, she guides these aspiring SaaS ventures to become finely tuned engines, poised to captivate investors and seize investment opportunities.
